text: Nashville SC is an American soccer team from Nashville, Tennessee, that has played in Major League Soccer (MLS) since the 2020 season. They started playing in 2018 as members of USL Championship. Nashville SC played at First Tennessee Park (2018–2019) and Nissan Stadium (2020–2021) before moving in to the new Geodis Park in 2022. == References == == Other websites == * The team's website Category:2010s establishments in Tennessee Category:Major League Soccer teams
